prHeadline: Mythic Expands Product Lineup with New Scalable, Power-Efficient Analog Matrix Processor for Edge AI Applications
headlineTxt: Jun 07, 2021, 09:00 ETMythic Expands Product Lineup with New Scalable, Power-Efficient Analog Matrix Processor for Edge AI Applicationsutilized.The M1076 AMP is ideal for video analytics workloads including object detection, classification, and depth estimation for industrial machine vision, autonomous drones, surveillance cameras, and network video recorders (NVRs) applications. The M1076 AMP can also support cutting-edge AR/VR applicationsMore news about: Mythic
